OL,5,G1600 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FA hot pursuit gets even hotter
OL,7,     Fwhen the pursuing car's brakes
OL,8,     Fcatch fire. A gadget allows
OL,9,     Fthieves to clone keyfob signals
OL,10,     Fremotely and steal cars without
OL,11,     Fthe keys.
OL,12,G1700 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FIt is Vicky's first pursuit, and
OL,14,     Fit doesn't disappoint. After a
OL,15,     Frace through Bradford, an Audi
OL,16,     Fslams into a parked car. The
OL,17,     Fdriver runs, but the car he
OL,18,     Fcrashed into has a secret.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
