OL,5,G2300 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FHeart-stopping emergencies on the
OL,7,     FM4 and Berkshire roads, as
OL,8,     Fparamedics battle to save a
OL,9,     Fcollapsed pensioner and a
OL,10,     Fcritically injured crash victim at
OL,11,     Fthe roadside.
OL,12,G0000 A&E After Dark
OL,13,     FFour men from Sudan are brought
OL,14,     Finto hospital by police, suspected
OL,15,     Fof being illegal immigrants, after
OL,16,     Fbeing found at the ferry port.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
