OL,5,G0100 #Text Me When You Get Home
OL,6,     FFourteen-year-old Deserae Turner
OL,7,     Fgoes missing after school,
OL,8,     Fprompting a frantic search and
OL,9,     Finvestigation that centred on her
OL,10,     FSnapchat account as the key to
OL,11,     Funraveling the mystery.
OL,12,G0155 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FTwo ladies keep Dr Dev Shah busy:
OL,14,     Fone has a large lipoma on her
OL,15,     Fback, the other a cyst on her
OL,16,     Fforehead. 19-year-old Abby hopes
OL,17,     FDr Natalia Spierings can rid her
OL,18,     Fof lumps on her ears.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
